<html lang="zh-Hant"><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">

<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>台中三日小旅行 | 6/17-6/19</title>
<style>
  :root {
    --bg: #FBF6EF;
    --bg-card: #FFFFFF;
    --ink: #3A2E26;
    --ink-soft: #6B5C4F;
    --rust: #C1622D;
    --rust-deep: #9C4A1F;
    --olive: #6E7A4F;
    --cream-line: #E8DCC8;
    --tag-bg: #F1E6D3;
    --shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(58,46,38,0.08);
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, "PingFang TC", "Noto Sans TC", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.6;
    padding-bottom: 60px;
  }

  /* Header */
  header {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--rust) 0%, var(--rust-deep) 100%);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 28px 20px 22px;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  header::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -30px; right: -30px;
    width: 140px; height: 140px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    border-radius: 50%;
  }
  header h1 {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
    position: relative;
  }
  header .sub {
    font-size: 13px;
    opacity: 0.92;
    margin-top: 6px;
    position: relative;
  }
  header .dates {
    display: inline-flex;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-size: 12px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.18);
    padding: 6px 14px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Sticky nav */
  nav {
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: var(--bg);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--cream-line);
    display: flex;
    overflow-x: auto;
    -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
    scrollbar-width: none;
  }
  nav::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  nav button {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    padding: 13px 16px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: inherit;
  }
  nav button.active {
    color: var(--rust);
    border-bottom-color: var(--rust);
  }

  main { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 18px 16px 0; }
  section { display: none; }
  section.active { display: block; animation: fadeIn 0.25s ease; }
  @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(4px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }

  /* Day card */
  .day-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border-radius: 14px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--cream-line);
  }
  .day-header {
    padding: 14px 18px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    background: var(--tag-bg);
  }
  .day-header .day-title {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--rust-deep);
  }
  .day-header .day-date {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .day-header .chevron {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--rust);
    transition: transform 0.25s ease;
  }
  .day-card.open .chevron { transform: rotate(180deg); }
  .day-body {
    max-height: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: max-height 0.3s ease;
  }
  .day-card.open .day-body { max-height: 3000px; }
  .day-body-inner { padding: 6px 18px 18px; }

  .timeline-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--cream-line);
  }
  .timeline-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .time-badge {
    flex: 0 0 56px;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--rust);
    padding-top: 2px;
  }
  .item-content { flex: 1; }
  .item-title {
    font-size: 14.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .item-note {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin-top: 3px;
  }
  .item-links {
    margin-top: 6px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    font-size: 11.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: var(--tag-bg);
    color: var(--rust-deep);
    border: 1px solid var(--cream-line);
  }
  .pill.map { background: #E9F0E0; color: var(--olive); }
  .tag-must {
    font-size: 10.5px;
    background: var(--rust);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 2px 7px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  /* Info sections */
  .info-block {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border-radius: 14px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    padding: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--cream-line);
  }
  .info-block h3 {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--rust-deep);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .info-row {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 8px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--cream-line);
    font-size: 13.5px;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .info-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .info-row .label { color: var(--ink-soft); flex: 0 0 auto; }
  .info-row .value { font-weight: 600; text-align: right; }

  .shop-card {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--rust);
    padding: 10px 0 10px 12px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .shop-card:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .shop-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: 14.5px; }
  .shop-meta { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink-soft); margin-top: 2px; }
  .shop-pick {
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-top: 6px;
    background: var(--tag-bg);
    padding: 8px 10px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .shop-pick b { color: var(--rust-deep); }

  .alert-box {
    background: #FBEFE3;
    border: 1px solid #E8C9A0;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--rust-deep);
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  /* Expense tracker */
  .expense-form {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border-radius: 14px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    padding: 18px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--cream-line);
  }
  .form-row {
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .form-row label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }
  .payer-toggle {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .payer-btn {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 12px;
    border: 2px solid var(--cream-line);
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: #fff;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: inherit;
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
  }
  .payer-btn.selected {
    border-color: var(--rust);
    background: var(--tag-bg);
    color: var(--rust-deep);
  }
  .form-row input[type="text"],
  .form-row input[type="number"] {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 11px 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--cream-line);
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-family: inherit;
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .form-row input:focus { outline: 2px solid var(--rust); outline-offset: 1px; }
  .split-toggle {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .split-btn {
    flex: 1;
    padding: 9px;
    border: 1px solid var(--cream-line);
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: #fff;
    font-size: 12.5px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: inherit;
  }
  .split-btn.selected {
    border-color: var(--olive);
    background: #E9F0E0;
    color: var(--olive);
  }
  .add-btn {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 13px;
    background: var(--rust);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 10px;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: inherit;
  }
  .add-btn:active { background: var(--rust-deep); }

  .summary-card {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--olive) 0%, #5A6440 100%);
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 20px 18px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }
  .summary-card .summary-label {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }
  .summary-card .summary-amount {
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 800;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }
  .summary-card .summary-sub {
    font-size: 12px;
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .expense-item {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 12px 14px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    border: 1px solid var(--cream-line);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .expense-item .exp-left { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .expense-item .exp-item-name {
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .expense-item .exp-meta {
    font-size: 11.5px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }
  .expense-item .exp-amount {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--rust-deep);
    flex: 0 0 auto;
  }
  .expense-item .exp-delete {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: #B5A89A;
    font-size: 18px;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 4px 6px;
  }
  .empty-state {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 13px;
    padding: 30px 10px;
  }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 12.5px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin: 18px 0 10px;
    padding-left: 2px;
  }

  footer {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    padding: 30px 20px 10px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1>台中三日小旅行</h1>
  <div class="sub">Old School 行旅 → 台中老爺酒店</div>
  <div class="dates">
    <span>🚄 6/17 (三) 19:31 台北出發</span>
    <span>🚄 6/19 (五) 19:08 台中回程</span>
  </div>
</header>

<nav id="tabs">
  <button class="active" data-tab="itinerary">📅 行程</button>
  <button data-tab="shops">🏪 店家攻略</button>
  <button data-tab="logistics">🛵 交通住宿</button>
  <button data-tab="expenses">💰 記帳</button>
</nav>

<main>

  <!-- ITINERARY -->
  <section id="itinerary" class="active">

    <div class="day-card open">
      <div class="day-header" onclick="toggleDay(this)">
        <div>
          <div class="day-title">Day 1 · 抵達夜</div>
          <div class="day-date">6/17（三）</div>
        </div>
        <div class="chevron">▾</div>
      </div>
      <div class="day-body">
        <div class="day-body-inner">

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="time-badge">19:31</div>
            <div class="item-content">
              <div class="item-title">高鐵台北出發</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="time-badge">~20:20</div>
            <div class="item-content">
              <div class="item-title">抵達台中高鐵站</div>
              <div class="item-note">車程約 50 分鐘</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="time-badge">20:45</div>
            <div class="item-content">
              <div class="item-title">入住 Old School 行旅 田中央旅店</div>
              <div class="item-note">台中車站步行約 5 分鐘</div>
              <div class="item-links">
                <a class="pill map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/?q=place_id:ChIJgRPi_z09aTQRAaFBd0Qic1E" target="_blank">📍 地圖</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="time-badge">20:30</div>
            <div class="item-content">
              <div class="item-title">一中街商圈晚餐</div>
              <div class="item-note">學生街排隊小吃、消夜選擇多</div>
              <div class="item-links">
                <a class="pill map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/?q=place_id:ChIJDf4N72g9aTQRMCr-EB0v0K0" target="_blank">📍 地圖</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="day-card open">
      <div class="day-header" onclick="toggleDay(this)">
        <div>
          <div class="day-title">Day 2 · 咖啡・古物・宵夜市</div>
          <div class="day-date">6/18（四）</div>
        </div>
        <div class="chevron">▾</div>
      </div>
      <div class="day-body">
        <div class="day-body-inner">

          <div class="alert-box">⚠️ 老賴紅茶週四公休，已排在 Day 3</div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="time-badge">早上</div>
            <div class="item-content">
              <div class="item-title">旅店早餐 → 租機車</div>
              <div class="item-note">推薦：車中寶台中火車站租機車（建國路159巷10號）</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="time-badge">09:00</div>
            <div class="item-content">
              <div class="item-title">Tamp Temper Coffee <span class="tag-must">必喝</span></div>
              <div class="item-note">評分 4.9，台中最強精品咖啡，老闆會介紹豆子產區</div>
              <div class="item-links">
                <a class="pill map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/?q=place_id:ChIJZ9bn9HQ9aTQRp2X0oIhCEhg" target="_blank">📍 地圖</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="time-badge">10:00</div>
            <div class="item-content">
              <div class="item-title">酷庫 kuku</div>
              <div class="item-note">老物古董雜貨店，巷弄裡藏寶，慢慢挖</div>
              <div class="item-links">
                <a class="pill map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/?q=place_id:ChIJFdoLOxM9aTQR7qP-cOhE5NM" target="_blank">📍 地圖</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="time-badge">12:00</div>
            <div class="item-content">
              <div class="item-title">饗食天堂 LaLaport 台中店 <span class="tag-must">已訂位</span></div>
              <div class="item-note">訂位編號 TCLA2026061811020</div>
              <div class="item-links">
                <a class="pill map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/?q=place_id:ChIJLZ62KYg9aTQRDca83mCUbvs" target="_blank">📍 地圖</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="time-badge">14:00</div>
            <div class="item-content">
              <div class="item-title">感傷唱片行 <span class="tag-must">必去</span></div>
              <div class="item-note">下午 1 點開門・黑膠卡帶＋咖啡甜點</div>
              <div class="item-links">
                <a class="pill map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/?q=place_id:ChIJK_NPkKY9aTQR9e-rjxvE2FU" target="_blank">📍 地圖</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="time-badge">16:00</div>
            <div class="item-content">
              <div class="item-title">Check-in 台中老爺酒店</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="time-badge">18:30</div>
            <div class="item-content">
              <div class="item-title">旱溪夜市晚餐</div>
              <div class="item-note">週四限定營業，在地人最愛的方塊型夜市</div>
              <div class="item-links">
                <a class="pill map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/?q=place_id:ChIJqaM87zc9aTQRg6mT2EhZ5vg" target="_blank">📍 地圖</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="day-card open">
      <div class="day-header" onclick="toggleDay(this)">
        <div>
          <div class="day-title">Day 3 · 老市場散步日</div>
          <div class="day-date">6/19（五）</div>
        </div>
        <div class="chevron">▾</div>
      </div>
      <div class="day-body">
        <div class="day-body-inner">

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="time-badge">早上</div>
            <div class="item-content">
              <div class="item-title">退房，行李寄放飯店或火車站</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="time-badge">上午</div>
            <div class="item-content">
              <div class="item-title">還機車</div>
              <div class="item-note">車中寶台中火車站租機車</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="time-badge">10:00</div>
            <div class="item-content">
              <div class="item-title">第二市場 + 老賴紅茶 <span class="tag-must">必喝</span></div>
              <div class="item-note">百年老市場、招牌紅茶現金交易，木瓜牛奶、菜頭粿也在這</div>
              <div class="item-links">
                <a class="pill map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/?q=place_id:ChIJn6lg0hI9aTQR96k14vG1Kic" target="_blank">📍 地圖</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="time-badge">11:30</div>
            <div class="item-content">
              <div class="item-title">光華小賣所</div>
              <div class="item-note">退役火車車廂改裝小店，台灣風T恤、茶葉蛋</div>
              <div class="item-links">
                <a class="pill map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/?q=place_id:ChIJJWiYTkQ9aTQRmJjbOILS-SA" target="_blank">📍 地圖</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="time-badge">12:30</div>
            <div class="item-content">
              <div class="item-title">Fusion Space 1962</div>
              <div class="item-note">舊化妝品工廠改建文創園區，咖啡廳、選物店適合悠閒拍照</div>
              <div class="item-links">
                <a class="pill map" href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/?q=place_id:ChIJGUN-HEo9aTQRUWNUBjjY2yY" target="_blank">📍 地圖</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="time-badge">傍晚</div>
            <div class="item-content">
              <div class="item-title">市區或火車站附近簡單用餐</div>
              <div class="item-note">取行李，準備搭車</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline-item">
            <div class="time-badge">19:08</div>
            <div class="item-content">
              <div class="item-title">高鐵離開台中</div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>

  <!-- SHOPS -->
  <section id="shops">

    <div class="info-block">
      <h3>☕ Tamp Temper Coffee</h3>
      <div class="shop-card">
        <div class="shop-meta">評分 4.9（1460+ 則評論）・週一至週五 9:00–17:30，週六 9:30–16:00，週日公休</div>
        <div class="shop-pick"><b>推薦：</b>單品手沖，老闆會主動介紹豆子產區與風味，空間迷你（2–3 個位子），純外帶也很方便。</div>
      </div>
